		{"id":"bf2c929c506d02d0","type":"text","text":"# Lattice dynamics \n\n## We make an hypothesis on the energy eigenvalues of the electronic problem instead of solving it","x":-680,"y":-80,"width":445,"height":200},
		{"id":"72d42619a110e6e6","type":"text","text":"# Harmonic approximation\n\n## We expand the functional form we decided for our potential up to 2nd order","x":-680,"y":160,"width":445,"height":171},
