		{"id":"aec52842f8c9f660","type":"text","text":"# From the phonon interpretation we can study the heat conduction as a non-equilibrium phenomenon using the Boltzmann transport equation","x":320,"y":1306,"width":440,"height":259},
		{"id":"9de1b932c4a933ab","type":"text","text":"## Sometimes, in order to predict experimental properties of solids we have to include higher terms in the expansion. We call these terms anharmonic terms","x":-1390,"y":-180,"width":425,"height":200},
